Build Fields Solver for Intel Xeon
----------------------------------

1) Adjust HDF5 root path in ../cmake/cmake_template.cmake.Xeon

2) Configure for compilation

   $ ./cmake-configure

3) Compile

   $ make

4) After successful compilation, the following files exist

   exec/iPic3D         (Particles solver - not used as particles solver runs on Xeon Phi)
   exec/iPic3D_fields  (Fields solver)
